data.description: This elegant home represents all that the community of Tuscany Hills represents!  From the moment you enter the home, you will feel like you've entered an Italian villa.  Travertine inlaid with granite flooring greets you at the front door.  The sophisticated living room immediately announces that you are ready to be entertained.  Look up at the Juliet style balcony.  Look straight through the home to view the most amazing back yard straight out of Roman photos.  There is a family room for casual gathering and the kitchen with the center island offers space to begin your cooking experience.  The formal dining room has a view of a relaxing water fountain.  Don't forget about the bedroom and full bathroom on the first floor.  But for a true experience, check out the movie theater-dedicated room. There's a stage and bilevel sitting area. It's frankly awesome!  Time to entertain and enjoy outside?  Check out the incredible pool and spa along with a stone fireplace and an entire area devoted to casual gathering around the Roman columns and marble statues with firepits.  Time for a drink or BBQ?  There is a huge built in bar and a cooking area.  Upstairs you will find FOUR more bedrooms PLUS three FULL bathrooms.  The primary ensuite seems to take up half of the upstairs living, but the guest bedrooms are spacious with large closets.  There is a cozy sitting room and an office area if you work from home.  This luxurious home will fit all of your needs from casual to elegant from first floor living to plenty of room for all upstairs.  This home is ready for you to move in and enjoy!
